title: 191. Andy & DJ CTI: School Eliminates D's & F's, Chicago Mayor Blames Retailers For Crime & NBA Vs. Freedom
itunes:title: 191. Andy & DJ CTI: School Eliminates D's & F's, Chicago Mayor Blames Retailers For Crime & NBA Vs. Freedom
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ discuss the California school district eliminating 'D' & 'F' grades, Chicago Mayor Lori Lightfoot placing blame on retailers for the increased crime & looting happening in the city, and the NBA begging Enes Kanter Freedom to take off his shoes that criticized China.
